{"build_type":"library","description":"One cooperative step of a summation fiber (computes sum n + (n-1) + ... + 0 via recursion through the scheduler). pc 0: if n < 1 the base case completes with result 0; otherwise it LAUNCHES a child summation fiber for n-1 (awaiter = self), enqueues it, and PARKS by setting pc 1 (it does not requeue itself). pc 1 (resumed after the child completed and its result was routed into child_result): result = n + child_result, then complete and route to the awaiter. Demonstrates launch, await, and stackless recursion entirely in scheduler state.","module_name":"advance-summation-fiber-within-cooperative-scheduler","package_name":"advance-summation-fiber-within-cooperative-scheduler","function_definitions":{"advance-summation-fiber-within-cooperative-scheduler":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"s","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"t","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"four","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"five","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"eight","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"fifty","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":50},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_